data.description: Welcome to your perfect family home! This spacious 5 bedroom, 3 bath property offers almost 3000 sq ft of living space. The open concept main level is great for entertaining with an island kitchen featuring granite countertops and a breakfast bar overlooking the cozy family room. A main level owner's ensuite with full bath and walk-in closet provides the ultimate in convenience, while an additional bedroom on this floor also has access to a full bath just outside the doorway. Upstairs you will find a bonus room plus three additional bedrooms, two sharing a Jack-n-Jill bathroom. Step outside onto your covered patio where you can relax or entertain while enjoying views of your spacious backyard! Plus, this home is located within walking distance to elementary school and neighborhood amenities including pool and playground make it even more attractive! Don't miss out—schedule your tour today!
